### =============================================
### Travel Booking App - API Tests
### =============================================

### VARIABLES
@localhost = http://localhost
@port = 3001
@baseUrl = {{localhost}}:{{port}}/api

### =============================================
### Test airports endpoint - search for JFK
GET {{baseUrl}}/airports?query=JFK

### Test airports endpoint - search for Los Angeles
GET {{baseUrl}}/airports?query=Los Angeles

### Test airports endpoint - search for London
GET {{baseUrl}}/airports?query=London

### =============================================
### Flight Search Tests
### =============================================

### One-way flight search - LAX DESTINATION
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=JFK&destinationLocationCode=LAX&departureDate=2026-05-20&adults=1


### One-way flight search - MADRID DESTINATION
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=JFK&destinationLocationCode=MAD&departureDate=2026-04-30&adults=1

### Round-trip flight search
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=JFK&destinationLocationCode=LAX&departureDate=2026-04-15&returnDate=2026-04-22&adults=1

### Flight search with multiple passengers
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=LAX&destinationLocationCode=LHR&departureDate=2026-05-01&adults=2&children=1

### Flight search with cabin class
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=SFO&destinationLocationCode=CDG&departureDate=2026-06-01&adults=1&cabinClass=FIRST

### Non-stop flights only
GET {{baseUrl}}/flight-search?originLocationCode=JFK&destinationLocationCode=MIA&departureDate=2026-04-10&adults=1&nonStop=true
